activities.message:
Hi @sp1d3rs,

Thank you very much for reporting this issue. I have patched the issue by adding `rel="noreferrer"` to all links and serving Google fonts locally.

```js
// File  website/assets/js/main.js, line 39
$(document).ready(function(){
	$("a").attr('rel','noreferrer');
});
```

```diff
- <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Inconsolata" rel="stylesheet">
+ <link href="{{ site.baseurl}}/assets/css/inconsolata.css">
```

I could potentially look into narrowing down the scope of the `redirect_uri`, but the current changes should suffice for the moment.

Could you please ensure that this resolves the issue that you reported?
